description: After years of making fantastic cupcakes for friends and family, Mrs. Thompson has taken her amazing skills on the road to serve them up to the people of Texas! Mrs Thompson's Most Wonderful Cupcakes is providing you with the best gourmet cupcakes you could ask for, so if you're looking for the perfect dessert for you or anybody you know, this is the truck for you!
name: Mrs. Thompson's Most Wonderful Cupcakes
